Create Datasets Directly from Microsoft Excel Spreadsheets

The Salesforce CRM Analytics Connector for Excel makes it easy to import data from Microsoft Excel 2013 to CRM Analytics.

The CRM Analytics Connector for Excel is available as an add-in for Excel 2013 on the desktop and Excel Online in Office 365. After you install the Connector just point and click to import data from Excel to CRM Analytics.

Considerations When Using theCRM Analytics Connector for Excel
To load Excel data when using a My Domain URL, save the data locally in .csv format, and then use the CRM Analytics .csv upload tool to load the data.
